304
00:18:36,083 --> 00:18:37,541
[Jin] Who's out there?

305
00:18:40,250 --> 00:18:41,625
[Kakizou] Answer me this:

306
00:18:41,708 --> 00:18:43,625
Where did you obtain
those coins you have?

307
00:18:43,708 --> 00:18:46,583
[Jin] As I suspected,
that money has a history.

308
00:18:46,666 --> 00:18:48,291
But I owe you no answer.

309
00:18:56,416 --> 00:18:57,041
My back.

310
00:18:57,125 --> 00:19:00,041
[Girl] Mmm, Master Jin.

311
00:19:21,666 --> 00:19:26,041
