to arrest them.

325
00:20:24,791 --> 00:20:26,208
We owe it all to you.

326
00:20:26,291 --> 00:20:27,125
[Mugen] Forget it.

327
00:20:27,208 --> 00:20:28,583
That guy was a scum bag.

328
00:20:28,666 --> 00:20:30,375
No thanks necessary.

329
00:20:30,458 --> 00:20:33,791
That is so long as you
intend on keeping your promise.

330
00:20:33,875 --> 00:20:35,291
Look! A naked woman!

331
00:20:35,375 --> 00:20:36,291
